    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/0494b19f6a289afa5162b911c9ff888e.avif?t=1711989925\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to Roll It To The End: A Minimalist Puzzle Challenge</strong><br><br>Embark on a journey of strategic contemplation with Roll It To The End, a game that encapsulates simplicity within its minimalist puzzle design.<br><br><strong>Discover the Right Path:</strong><br>Uncover the intricacies of each level as you meticulously navigate the terrain. Precision in your movements is crucial to unlocking the path to success.<br><br><strong>Objective: Reach the End:</strong><br>Your ultimate goal is clear – reach the endpoint by skillfully matching the number at the bottom of the dice with the designated endpoint value.<br><br><strong>Deceptively Simple:</strong><br>At first glance, the game may appear straightforward. However, as you progress, the introduction of rolling tiles, intricate platforms, gates, buttons, and the ticking clock adds layers of complexity.<br><br><strong>Challenge Awaits:</strong><br>Tiles and platforms introduce dynamic movement, gates and buttons trigger events, and elements like points and time constraints heighten the challenge. Each level becomes a puzzle to unravel.<br><br><strong>Mastering Complexity:</strong><br>Fear not the increasing intricacy. With a strategic mindset, you can conquer the complications and gracefully navigate through each level to reach your destination.<br><br><strong>Roll It To The End: Where Simplicity Meets Complexity, and Strategy Prevails.</strong><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/6fe902ff5e3b7bfc2bcf6c5aa7fb9ea4.avif?t=1711989925\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br><br><strong>1. Diverse Tiles and Platforms:</strong><br>Encounter an extensive array of both normal and special tiles/platforms, featuring traps, gates, portals, and utilities. Each element introduces unique challenges to enhance gameplay.<br><br><strong>2. Dice Customizer:</strong><br>Elevate your gaming experience with the <strong>Dice Customizer</strong>. Modify your dice's 3D model and exercise complete control over its appearance, including <strong>RGB</strong>, <strong>Metallic</strong>, <strong>Roughness</strong>, and <strong>Emissive</strong> attributes.<br><br><strong>3. Dynamic Level Builder:</strong><br>Unleash your creativity using the <strong>Level Builder</strong>, where you can craft and customize your own levels. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/531fbaeef25034396d7e05443d15a349.avif?t=1711989925\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/945649f2ecf9e1dfecbb4018f666d985.avif?t=1711989925\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/edb7d71bdd477301ef027970cfbed0a2.poster.avif?t=1711989925\" width=300 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/edb7d71bdd477301ef027970cfbed0a2.webm?t=1711989925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/edb7d71bdd477301ef027970cfbed0a2.mp4?t=1711989925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362570/extras/14ce4db62b081caffadeec448590f9cf.poster.avif?t=1711989925\" width=300 height=94 ><source